works.description: “My published post, “Johnny Depp and Vanessa Paradis: Breakup In the Works?”, is infringed by the text excerpted on the site, beginning with the text "Rumors have been circulating about the possibility of a breakup between Johnny Depp and his longtime girlfriend and baby mama, Vanessa Paradis, for several months now."

My published post, “JWoww, Tim Tebow and Paula Deen Wanted on Dancing With the Stars”, is infringed by the text excerpted on the site, beginning with the text "The next season of Dancing With the Stars is destined to be one of the series' best if producers are able to land the talent they seek."
